reviewText: This TV series was funny as hell. From start to final episode. I laugh my head off.but I was really upset it didn't make for a second season.

My wife and I loved the show.  But when I ordered it, the DVD version we received was made for a different region than the USA and we had to return it.  Not sure why you all can't sell this series in a version playable on USA DVD players!!!  We'd immediately buy it if available.
